parameters:
Noble Echizo: I'm currently on vacation, so please don't
disturb me.
Clea: I checked the bulletin board.

Noble Etizo: Oh, you've come! I want you to listen to an
adventure story from my only son.

Noble Etizo: I may be seen as a doting parent, but my son
is highly intelligent and impeccable as a successor.

Noble Etizo: Perhaps because of that, he doesn't have any
friends of the same age and tends to be a shut-in. Lately,
his attitude towards his wife has also become aggressive...

Noble Etizo: I want you to listen to an adventure story and
let him know about the vast world.

Thief Nora: In that case, dragon subjugation would be
perfect!

Noble Etizo: That green cloak... Could it be Claire from
the Adventurer's Guild!
Clea: Yes, I can talk about dragon subjugation.

Noble Etizo: It is the guidance of the Supreme God Sol!
Please, I want you to tell Amel an adventure tale, no, a
hero's tale!

Noble Lady Ram: You, it seems you're not in the villa after
all...
Thief Nora: We'll go search for him ourselves!

Noble Etizo: I apologize, but please take care of us,
heroes.
Clea: Yes, leave it to me.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Noble Etizo: Please help me search for my son.

Noble Etizo: Thank you for finding my son! Let's have a
meal and talk, although it may be modest!

Clea: We headed out with our fellow adventurers from the
Adventurer's Guild, as well as the Imperial Army led by
General Atu and our friends.

Noble Etizo: I know, it's Mount Monimos, where the legend
of the brave heroes took place!
Lady Ram, You, in the middle of the conversation!

Thief Nora: It was amazing, flying ships in the sky and
diving into hordes of monsters!
Thief Nora: So, so, what else--

Noble Etizo: Hey, Amel! Where do you think you're going
when we have guests!
Noble Amel: Hmph, you're like a lying bard.

Thief Nora: D-Did I do something to make them dislike
me...?

Mage Relm: I suppose it's that age, isn't it? Even I, as an
adult, went through that phase!
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, we don't mind at all.

Noble Etizo: I believe that sometimes rough methods are
necessary. In such cases, I hope that everyone will be
willing to cooperate.

Noble Etizo: Please take a look at the bulletin board when
you have some time.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Echizo: Perhaps this is the result of spoiling him,
but I believe we should ask for your cooperation in helping
our son change his ways.

Noble Etizo: Please allow me to consult with you regarding
my son. I have finally decided to undergo radical treatment
for Amel's sake.

Noble Etizo: I would like all of you to cross through the
forest that I own as Amel's escorts.

Mage Relm: Crossing through the forest... How does that
relate to radical treatment?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, does that mean we have a role to
intimidate?

Noble Etizo: That's right! I want you to know fear and
understand what you must overcome.
Thief Nora: Ugh... I feel a little sorry for him.

Clea: Is it possible to have a discussion with the ones we
are supposed to intimidate beforehand?

Noble Etizo: I had intended to hire someone separate from
all of you, but I lost contact with them at some point...
Noble Etizo: Would you be willing to take on this task?

Clea: I think it's suitable for making accurate situational
judgments in the forest.

Mage Relm: I agree, but it seems a bit intimidating... you
know?

Thief Nora: Grrr! I'm gonna eat you up! Ahaha... Is this
not good enough...?

Priestess Sophia: How about going with powerful outfits?
You might be able to transform from cute girls to cute
beasts, you know?

Noble Etizo: I'll leave the details to all of you. Please
let me know when you're ready to go to the forest.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Echizo: I am a fake guard, but our destination is the
forest. Are you truly prepared?

Noble Echizo: I will convey it to Amel. Please take care of
Amel for me.
3後order：クエスト指令開始「盗賊ノラが悪魔レフガリアの礼装を装備して貴族エチゾに話す」
条件を満たしていないときのメッセージがないので仮置き
Noble Echizo: Welcome back! How is Amel doing?

Noble Echizo: The thieves from the Aspida Alliance!? They
have the audacity to trespass on my land again!

Clea: We have repelled the thieves and Amel-kun is
unharmed.

Amel, the noble's son: I'm really sorry for everything.
It's because of me that I put everyone in danger.

Noble Echizo: Oh, as expected of the Dragon Slayer! Not
only have you had a change of heart, but you have also saved
our lives!

Noble Echizo: I will give you a reward that exceeds our
promised agreement.

Noble Echizo: Now, let's resume your education as the
heir!
Thief Nora: Um... Is it okay?

Thief Nora: Amel-kun was feeling lonely... so please talk
to him not as a successor, but as a friend.
Thief Nora: S-Sorry for being cheeky...
Noble Echizo: Is that so, Amel?
Noble's son Amel: Yes... as my sister says.

Noble Echizo: ...This is a villa, let's spend time here as
just a family.

Noble Echizo: Thank you for saying something difficult. It
seems that Amel has become very fond of you.
Noble Echizo: What happened in the forest?

Thief Nora: That's a secret between just the two of us,
right?

Noble Echizo: ...Yes, that is a secret between the two of
them.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Noble Etizo: I have learned from all of you. From now on, I
want to have a proper conversation with my son.

Lady Ram, the noblewoman: I wonder if you saw a little boy?
That child... We came all the way to the vacation home as a
family, and yet...

Lady Ram, I wonder if that child... is really going to be
okay.

Lady Ram, the noblewoman: I apologize for my son's
behavior. He is actually a good and obedient child, please
believe me.

Lady Ram, the noblewoman: Thank you for saving my son. I
may be a useless mother, but from now on, I will face Amel
and take care of him.
